3. National Institute of Korean Language (국립국어원) Open API dictionaries
   (queried by bin/krdict — no data is bundled, only API calls at runtime)
================================================================================
  - 표준국어대사전  Standard Korean Dictionary   https://stdict.korean.go.kr
  - 우리말샘        Urimalsaem (open dictionary)  https://opendict.korean.go.kr
  - 한국어기초사전  Korean Learners' Dictionary   https://krdict.korean.go.kr

  These are public Open API services operated by 국립국어원. Each requires the
  end user to register and obtain their OWN free authentication key. This
  project ships NO keys and stores NO dictionary data; it only formats the
  responses returned to the user's own key at runtime. Dictionary content is
  © National Institute of Korean Language and subject to its terms of use.

